"ùêåùêÄùêòùêÄùêäùêé ùêÇùêáùêàùêçùêé" Teleserial is a female-dominated telefilm that seeks to portray the reality of what is happening in society. How many children are orphaned in Nepal due to the distortion and inconsistency in love relationships.

"MAYAKO CHINO " is a telefilm that seeks to show the impact of interracial love affair on society between rich and poor.

Getting education is a child's right, but many children in Nepal have not been able to go to school because they do not have good parents.

   The caterpillar of the tele-serial, Kamala, who herself has struggled a lot to read and will go on a separate campaign tomorrow to teach such children who do not have good parents.

en.description:
"ùêåùêÄùêòùêÄùêäùêé ùêÇùêáùêàùêçùêé" Teleserial is a female-dominated telefilm that seeks to portray the reality of what is happening in society. How many children are orphaned in Nepal due to the distortion and inconsistency in love relationships.

"MAYAKO CHINO " is a telefilm that seeks to show the impact of interracial love affair on society between rich and poor.

Getting education is a child's right, but many children in Nepal have not been able to go to school because they do not have good parents.

   The caterpillar of the tele-serial, Kamala, who herself has struggled a lot to read and will go on a separate campaign tomorrow to teach such children who do not have good parents.

snippet.description:
Dream Girl ki duniya mein get ready for a rib-tickling kahaani of your sapnon ki rani! ü§©üòÜ

#DreamGirl2Trailer Out Now! 

#25AugustHogaMast
#DreamGirl2 in Cinemas on 25th August.

Tab tak ke liye follow kariyega apni Pooja ko on Instagram and Twitter - 

Instagram - https://instagram.com/pooja___dreamgirl
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Pooja_DreamGirl 

Karam, a small-town boy from Mathura, is struggling every day to pay his father's debt, who has borrowed money from nearly everyone on the planet. On the other hand, he is deeply in love with Pari, whose father has kept the conditions to marry her. To make ends meet, Karam dons as Pooja, which creates wild chaos and a comedy of errors. 

Dream Girl 2 is a rib-tickling and hilariously entertaining story with a compelling ensemble including Annu Kapoor, Paresh Rawal, Vijay Raaz, Rajpal Yadav, Asrani Saab, Manoj Joshi, Abhishek Banerjee, Seema Pahwa, Manjot Singh, Ranjan Raj among many others.
